         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Settlement is a period end closing process that allocates the actual costs of a project that were posted during the month from a WBS element to  Assets Under Construction and/or cost centers.  During periodic settlement, the actual costs on the order or WBS element are allocated completely or partially to one or more receivers."/>
